Archive-Simple

A simple archive for pure perl packages.

INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

    perl Build.PL
    ./Build
    ./Build test
    ./Build install

SUPPORT AND DOCUMENTATION

After installing, you can find documentation for this module with the
perldoc command.

    perldoc Archive::Simple

You can also look for information at:

    RT, CPAN's request tracker
        http://rt.cpan.org/NoAuth/Bugs.html?Dist=Archive-Simple

    AnnoCPAN, Annotated CPAN documentation
        http://annocpan.org/dist/Archive-Simple

    CPAN Ratings
        http://cpanratings.perl.org/d/Archive-Simple

    Search CPAN
        http://search.cpan.org/dist/Archive-Simple/

    Source Code
        git://github.com/ivanwills/Archive-Simple.git

